subtitleNullable: Hourly instances for river flow observations of eight sites
descriptionNullable:
The RF2 dataset extends the [RF1](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/samanemami/river-flowrf1)data by adding precipitation forecast information for each of the 8 sites.

To have more information about this dataset, you may review the [RF1](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/samanemami/river-flowrf1) first.

Basic information of the dataset is stored [here](https://www.kaggle.com/code/samanemami/river-flow-2-datasets).
